  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK408">
<l>nallārkaṭ paṭṭa vaṟumaiyi ṉiṉṉātē</l>
<l>kallārkaṭ paṭṭa tiru</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wealth, gained by the unlearned, will give more sorrow than the poverty which may come upon the learned.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
